metadata.name: B10M1NDS
metadata.description: B10M1NDS are a representation of the symbiotic conflux of the organic, the inorganic and the nurturing tension of their counterpoise. The figures, made of enduring stone, metal and wood, seem to draw sentience and an ancient remembrance from the interlacing flora. These solid yet vulnerable vignettes hearken to a pre- or post-transhumanistic time while offering their silent soliloquy on the present.
